- **Philosophy**
- **Color Palette**
  - Backgrounds / Borders / Text / Accents (and Semantic colors if needed)
- **Typography**
  - Font family + scale (sizes/weights/line-height/tracking)
- **Components**
  - Buttons, Cards, Inputs, Badges (and any custom components)
- **Layout principles**
- **Animation / interaction rules**

Notes:

- Prefer concrete values (hex/rgba, px/rem, durations).
- The showcase generator expects these tokens to map into `page.tsx` + `preview.tsx`.
